{
  "title": "Gloriously Rich Italian Beef Risotto",
  "description": "A rich and creamy Italian dish featuring vanilla extract and rest-meat, perfect for special occasions, and can be adapted to be plant-based friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
